  "title": "Pre-school Centre Admin (East, up to $3,300)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Coordinate centre schedules, events, enrichment programmes, and logistics.</li>\n  <li>Manage procurement, inventory, and vendor coordination.</li>\n  <li>Generate and issue monthly school fee invoices to parents.</li>\n  <li>Manage refund processes and documentation.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Higher Nitec and above</li>\n  <li>At least 2 years of <strong>administrative experience</strong> in a <strong>pre-school setting.</strong></li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and customer service skills.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
